            verse = 28,
            text = "समं पश्यन्हि सर्वत्र समवस्थितमीश्वरम् |\nन हिनस्त्यात्मनात्मानं ततो याति परां गतिम् || २८ ||",
            transliteration = "samaṁ paśyan hi sarvatra samavasthitam īśvaram\nna hinasty ātmanātmānaṁ tato yāti parāṁ gatim",
            englishTranslation = "One who sees the Supreme Lord equally present in all living beings does not degrade himself through his mind; thus he attains the supreme destination.",
